								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>61 folios (+ 3 paper flyleaves at the beginning and 2 at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires of originally 10 leaves each, only nos. 15-16 are complete. </p>
									<p>Signatures of Arabic words in the left-hand upper corner of the first page, for the most part not preserved. </p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Number of pages damaged and stained. </p>
									<p>Slightly worm-eaten. </p>
									<p>Gaps after folio 1, 9, 11, 12, 13, 15, 16, 25, 28, 29, 31 and 53. </p>
									<p>Imperfect at the beginning and at the end. </p>
